quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  7,184,"Ana ngaakuchetelela? Mwa n'jaomotu mwangali masoka, nganaŵa jwalakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ikaŵeje nkutetela jwakuonechela."
  7,185,"Ana ngaakuuona uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka, ni ichindu yosope yaagumbile Allah, soni yanti mwine komboleka kuŵa ndaŵi jao jakuwila jiŵandichile? Ana ni abalichi panyuma paaji (Quraniji) jatachijikulupilila?"
  7,186,"Mundu jwannechelele Allah kusokonechela, basi nganakola nkun'jongola, ni akwalekaga nkusokonechela mwaomo achiyumbagayumbaga."
  9,88,"Nambo Ntenga ﷺ ni aŵala ŵakulupilile najo imo, aputile ngondo ni chipanje chao ni achimisyene ŵakwe, soni ŵanganyao akwete kupata yambone, soni ŵanyao ni ŵali ŵakupunda."
  9,89,"Allah jwalinganyichisye ŵanganyao Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo, chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo, kwele ni kupunda kwekulungwa nnope."
  9,90,"Soni akutola ipaka (yakuona) mu ŵarabu ŵanchimisi ŵayiche (kwa Ntenga ﷺ) kuti apedwe lusa (lwangajaula kungondo), nambo aŵala (achinakunaku) ŵaŵannambwisye Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, ŵagambile kutama (mwangali kuŵenda lusa kwa Ntenga ﷺ), chiyapate aŵala ŵakanile mwa jamanjao ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope."
  10,46,"Soni kanga chitunnosye (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ pa duniya pepano) ine mwa ayila (ipotesi) yatukwatetela kapena kumpa chiwa (nkanitunnosye tiyapatepe), basi Kukwetu ni kwakuujila kwao, soni Allah ni Mboni pa yaakutenda."
  10,47,"Soni nkutula uliose ukwete ntenga, basi pandema jatachiyika ntenga jwao (ku Kiyama) kuchilamulidwa chilikati chao mwa chilungamiko, soni ŵanganyao ngasatendedwa lupuso."
  10,48,"Sano ni akutiji: “Ana chele chilangachi chiyiche chakachi nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona?”"
  11,13,"Kapena ŵanganyao akuti: “Jwalakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nijwaajitunjile (Qur’aniji)?” Jilani: “Basi ikani nasyo sura likumi syakulandana najo nisili syakutungwa, nimwaŵilanje ŵatinkombole (kwaŵilanga kuti ankamuchisye) ŵangaŵaga Allah nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  11,14,"“Nambo naga akan’jitika ŵanganyammwe (ŵakwaŵilanga kuti ankamuchisyeo), basi manyililani yanti (Qur’anijo) jitulusyidwe mwa umanyilisi wa Allah, ni kuti pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, ana nambi jenumanja chim’be Asilamu?”"
  11,15,"Ŵaliose ŵaakusaka umi wa duniya ni ipeto yakwe, chitwakwanichisye (malipilo ga) itendo yao pa duniya pepo, soni ŵanganyao palakwepo ngaaŵa ŵakupungusyidwa (kalikose)."